    <article class="prose">
      <p>
        By using cards.oriz.in or any <code>*.oriz.in</code> site, you agree
        to these terms. They are short on purpose.
      </p>

      <h2>Use the sites lawfully</h2>
      <p>
        Don't try to break the sites, scrape them at abusive rates, or use them
        to harass others. Account takeover, copyright infringement, and any
        activity prohibited under Indian law are forbidden.
      </p>

      <h2>Content is provided as-is</h2>
      <p>
        Card profiles, fees, and rewards data on cards.oriz.in are provided
        for information and convenience only. They are <strong>not</strong>
        financial advice and may lag the bank's own terms by days or weeks.
